63_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_4406f2be-2a5c-45ef-8662-c962d6c28312" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref> does not provide access to or egress for, and is separated from, the extra <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_91834c0d-4a3f-4d05-9ef9-6d83f7d1a5c2" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> by construction having—<ol><li>an FRL of –/60/60, if non-<xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1360_0.4.0.xml#_fe6e68c5-3fcb-4038-844a-2fcb7099f7da" id="_fe918758-5a04-4995-abd3-56cebe8361b1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">loadbearing</xref>; and</li><li>an FRL of 90/90/90 for Type A construction or 60/60/60 for Type B or C construction, if <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1360_0.4.0.xml#_fe6e68c5-3fcb-4038-844a-2fcb7099f7da" id="_31eb03f0-bda6-495c-8859-27c4ac93962a" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">loadbearing</xref>; and</li><li>no opening that could permit the passage of fire or smoke.</li></ol></li></ol></li></ol><subclause id="_57160f26-ce44-46f9-b1ee-1d95d1c49207" outputclass="state-variation" variation="SA" variation-type="REPLACE"><title id="_c5de9595-cd6e-4f0e-9490-6216cc713d4b">SA REPLACE SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Class 5, 6, 7, 8 or 9 buildings — Every stairway or ramp serving as a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_485e2004-0b3e-48d1-8c1f-fb57ccfdb6c7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_8cd3f7aa-bff3-44f9-bf93-829dd21b9cb5" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref> must be fire-isolated unless—</p><ol ou